title: Sliders Collection (1996 - 1997)
description:
Sliders Collection (1996 - 1997)


The Sliders are a group of four individuals who travels to different parallel universes by the use of a timer. A college genius named Quinn Mallory invented the timer and brought along with his girlfriend, Wade Welles, his college professor, Arturo and accidentally brought the singer, Rembrandt Brown also known as Cryin' Man. Now the Sliders must find their way back home while travelling to each Earth and facing unknown dangers.
